name: Wr.makan jawa WIDADARI
address: Jl. Raya Denpasar - Gilimanuk No.14, Antap, Kec. Selemadeg, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82162, Indonesia
review 1: Good place to rest. Opposite Petrol station. O felt a little overcharged as we ordered 2x Ayam Nasi and a bottle of coke and it was 48k
review 2: The stuff will rip you off as much as they can. I ordered noodles and a drink which costed 10 000 and 6 000 respectively. After giving a 100 000 I received 40 000 back. The stuff insisted my taxi driver bought cigarettes and makes me pay for them. After checking with the driver, the stuff brings me back another 10 000 which still doesn’t add up to the change I should’ve received; the waitress then tries to lie about the price of the food ordered. She then discusses with another waitress and laughs, pulls out another 5 000 which still isn’t enough. Frustrated with the insanity I leave the restaurant, completely ripped off and disrespected. Do yourself a favor and don’t go there.
